![Working on my next 3D printer. Yes, the AB motors are the wrong way.](/images/micron/micron_assembly_progress.jpg)

# Stuff

* [LDO Micron+ kit][]
* [LDO Colony Clacker][] door kit
* [neXtG Fiber Hotend][] (no hotend included in the LDO kit)
* [Beacon probe][] (best quality of life upgrade IMO)
* Chamber thermistor and bed fans (standard but not included in the LDO kit)
* Polymaker Polylite ASA [Yellow][] & [Teal][] for printed parts

