# Gantry and Z assembly

![](/images/micron/xy_assembly.jpg)

![](/images/micron/z_gantry_assembly.jpg)

![](/images/micron/micron_with_gantry.jpg)

At this point I noticed that I installed the AB motors the wrong way.
I had to remove the belts, the gantry, flip the motors, and assemble them again.
Fun times.

